The final EFA included 25 items that loaded on five factors, which explain 70.3% of the variability in HPV vaccine-seeking behaviors in adults. These factors included the following:
Factor 1: Benefits/Trust;
Factor 2: Perceived Susceptibility;
Factor 3: Attitudes/Behavioral Control;
Factor 4: Perceived Barriers;
Factor 5: Perceived Severity.
